                                </svg>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- What I Do Section -->
            <section class="mb-16 scroll-mt-24" id="what-i-do">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white">What I Do</h2>
                    <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-800 ml-6"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-amber-500 text-xl mt-1">trending_up</span>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Promote Predictable Delivery</h4>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">I help teams deliver better outcomes, faster, and more predictably by replacing dysfunctional, wasteful agile practices with value-adding activities and continuous improvement.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-500 text-xl mt-1">rocket_launch</span>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Launch Complex Programs</h4>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">I help organizations run successful, high-stakes programs by breaking down ambiguous large-scale initiatives, aligning cross-functional stakeholders around a shared understanding, clear domain boundaries, and realistic delivery plans.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-500 text-xl mt-1">groups</span>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Empower Teams</h4>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">I focus on building trust-based, high-performance environments where decision-making authority is moved to the team level, empowering them to solve their own challenges, remove delays and deliver higher-quality outcomes.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-purple-500 text-xl mt-1">settings</span>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Sociotechnical Design</h4>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Applying Team Topologies and Domain-Driven Design to ensure team structures are optimized for flow and reduced cognitive load.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Product & Technical Delivery Highlights -->
            <section class="mb-16 scroll-mt-24" id="delivery-highlights">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Product & Technical Delivery Highlights</h2>
                    <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-800 ml-6"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div class="p-6 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 rounded-lg">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-amber-500">account_balance</span>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Core Banking & Payments</h4>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Supported the delivery of payment platforms, fraud systems, cross-border cash management solutions, and API services for financial institutions.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-6 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 rounded-lg">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-500">database</span>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Data & Compliance</h4>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Guided teams in building Wealth Management Data Lake, supporting AML, KYC, and Fraud stakeholders.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-6 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 rounded-lg">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-500">api</span>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Open Banking & BaaS</h4>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Facilitated the discovery and development of Open Banking APIs for Account Validation, Track & Trace, and real-time transaction monitoring.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-6 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 rounded-lg">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-purple-500">devices</span>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Digital Experience</h4>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Supported the delivery of new features for Direct Investing/Online Trading platforms and the implementation of a major specialized Salesforce instance for a banking line of business.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-6 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 rounded-lg">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-red-500">local_pharmacy</span>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">HealthTech</h4>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Supported the delivery of a new Pharmacy Management System.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-6 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 rounded-lg">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-cyan-500">hub</span>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">FinTech Ecosystems</h4>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Supported integrations with financial data aggregators, accounting software, and Earned Wage Access (EWA) providers.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Experience Section -->
            <section class="mb-16 scroll-mt-24" id="experience">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-12">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Experience</h2>
                    <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-800 ml-6"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="space-y-12">
                    <!-- Agile by Design -->
                    <div class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800">
                        <div class="absolute -left-0.5 top-0 w-0.5 h-1.5 bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark"></div>
                        <div class="absolute -left-2 top-1.5 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-primary ring-4 ring-white dark:ring-background-dark"></div>
                        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-baseline justify-between mb-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Senior Agile Coach / Agile Coach</h3>
                            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary dark:text-blue-400">2017 — Present</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="pb-6 border-b border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Agile by Design</h4>

                            <div class="space-y-6">
                                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                                    Senior Agile SME and Transformation Coach with a focus on <strong>Wealth, Payments, and Healthcare</strong>. Expert in <strong>sociotechnical design</strong>, organizational flow, and creating the conditions for <strong>high-performing teams</strong>.
                                </p>

                                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                                    <div>
                                        <h5 class="font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-amber-500 text-lg">workspace_premium</span>
                                            Program Delivery
                                        </h5>
                                        <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 space-y-1.5">
                                            <li>• Led delivery of high-scale systems and platforms across financial services, healthcare, and technology domains</li>
                                            <li>• Served as lead coach for large-scale initiatives, training and coordinating multiple <strong>cross-functional teams</strong></li>
                                            <li>• Facilitated <strong>collaborative modeling</strong> workshops to align stakeholders around complex systems</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>

                                    <div>
                                        <h5 class="font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-500 text-lg">account_tree</span>
                                            Organizational Design
                                        </h5>
                                        <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 space-y-1.5">
                                            <li>• Designed operating models for enterprise service lines using modern organizational patterns</li>
                                            <li>• Coached large organizations through structural and cultural transformations</li>
                                            <li>• Applied <strong>Domain-Driven Design</strong> and sociotechnical principles to improve team effectiveness</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>

                                    <div>
                                        <h5 class="font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-500 text-lg">query_stats</span>
                                            Forecasting & Flow
                                        </h5>
                                        <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 space-y-1.5">
                                            <li>• Replaced guess-based planning with <strong>probabilistic forecasting</strong> to provide data-driven delivery commitments</li>
                                            <li>• Mapped and optimized <strong>value streams</strong> to accelerate delivery and reduce time-to-market</li>
                                            <li>• Created <strong>portfolio management</strong> systems linking strategy to daily execution</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>

                                    <div>
                                        <h5 class="font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-cyan-500 text-lg">groups</span>
                                            Coaching & Training
                                        </h5>
                                        <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 space-y-1.5">
                                            <li>• Provided <strong>cross-functional</strong> coaching to a range of roles, including Architects, Software Developers, Directors, and Product Owners
                                            <li>• Designed and led training programs on <strong>agile methodologies</strong>, flow, and <strong>product discovery</strong></li>
                                            <li>• Introduced experimentation frameworks to accelerate learning and validate assumptions</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Data Analyst -->
                    <div class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800">
                        <div class="absolute -left-0.5 top-0 w-0.5 h-1.5 bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark"></div>
                        <div class="absolute -left-2 top-1.5 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-slate-300 dark:bg-slate-700 ring-4 ring-white dark:ring-background-dark"></div>
                        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-baseline justify-between mb-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Data Analyst</h3>
                            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-400">2013 — 2017</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="pb-6 border-b border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Rubicon Project</h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                                Leveraged data analytics and quantitative methods to support campaign optimization and client reporting within the digital advertising ecosystem.
                            </p>
                        </div>
